  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "System Lead (SATCOM)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is seeking a Technical Lead with strong experience in SATCOM system integration to support presales solutioning and project delivery. The role focuses on end-to-end SATCOM design, integration, testing, and commissioning for mission-critical systems.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Design, integrate, and commission SATCOM and network systems</li><li>Translate project requirements into SATCOM architectures and solutions</li><li>Conduct technical reviews, PoCs, testing, and troubleshooting</li><li>Support customer engagements and maintain project documentation</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>6+ years’ experience in SATCOM or related industries</li><li>Hands-on experience with SATCOM terminals, RF equipment, and link budget analysis</li><li>Experience with satellite modems (e.g. iDirect) and test equipment</li><li>Strong analytical, troubleshooting, and communication skills</li><li>Experience in large-scale project delivery</li><li>Singaporeans only | Location: Ang Mo Kio</li></ul><p><strong>To apply</strong><br /><br />To apply or find out more information on this role, please email us or send in your updated resume to:<br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lynn.tay@starcareerconsulting.com</a></p><p><strong>Lynn Tay</strong> (Reg. No. R1876711)<br /><strong>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD</strong> (EA Licence: 20C0353)<br /></p>",
